"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"最近思考了下如何利用好这片区域，产生了三个想法，目前整个系统只能算个在线写作平台，不过我想随着完善，能真正去中心化。\\n\\n1、工业领域的知识搬家\\n\\n包含个人知识的总结，有用知识的分类\\n\\n2、元知识的汇总\\n\\n3、所有梦境的描述\\n\\n当我想到建立自己永存的知识库时，发现一个问题。提纲式存储还非常简陋，只能基本的文本存储。\",\"timestamp\":1635597176,\"title\":\"这片区域以后的计划\"},\"digest\":\"dJ93OuB7ihZilNnxmLHOQoLA1QcTXfwLVBXT_EJwKkM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x63bF83c11c50627F44119336A3c2f616b7c65228\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"UJyJZnvTvWk6jtEFrgyhM8tYCnQxXBw9382YwR3rM5s\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"1n5U0BWxr49voz8_UGdniiQ9E4Z5MaCQlSt4RK0Jp20\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"-U7UVUWhq27NElXm5Yab4HyzWAm_DByqTNKgQkEVn93CD9oRYtSVuKVuewFKytmMI6cLZx9Mt7yvphTNrm2zPQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x2e3d7395faa25632a15e488406433fb4c3a00a908ec10906e1adae26e99a17c368a16357f44d403ed91961abff51f4fc61af8b79a2eaafda2c33ff40fa1680cc1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"UJyJZnvTvWk6jtEFrgyhM8tYCnQxXBw9382YwR3rM5s\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"1n5U0BWxr49voz8_UGdniiQ9E4Z5MaCQlSt4RK0Jp20\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"dJ93OuB7ihZilNnxmLHOQoLA1QcTXfwLVBXT_EJwKkM\"}"